summary:
theedgemalaysia.com highlighted four stocks with momentum at Bursa Malaysia’s noon market break on Monday, with three showing positive momentum and one stock showing negative momentum.    

The stocks with positive momentum were:    


	    SDS Group Berhad (KL:SDS) — down 2.5 sen or 2.67% at 91 sen;  
	    Pegasus Heights Berhad (KL:PHB) — unchanged at 10 sen;  
	    Engtex Group Bhd (KL:ENGTEX) — down five sen or 3.82% at RM1.26.
